seller.description: With 7+ years experience in Graphic Design, and specialization in Product Artwork, I design creative and best selling product labels and packaging for clients from Amazon and other leading e-commerce websites. My impressive, top-notch and pixel perfect designs are sure to boost your product sales by making your product stand out and land right into your customer’s cart!

reviews.comment: My team had initially hired another designer to create our packaging label. Unfortunately, we were not happy with the design that was produce, so we hired Asahab to work on a redesign. Asahab skillfully took the initial design and requirements, and with expert precision, crafted a redesigned label that exceeded our expectations. We couldn't be more pleased with the results. A well-deserved 5 stars!

Asahab has always created FANTASTIC work for my team! He takes our ideas and really makes them shine. He is always fast and willing to work with anything that comes up. I will always use him because he truly sees our vision.
the font is unique, fits the space needed for social media. readable. creative to keep it feminine. with enterchange of cameras this will be perfect.

This was the best delivery I have gotten from any designer on Fiverr. He was very polite, understood exactly what I wanted, and was always happy to make revisions to make sure that the work was exactly as I wanted it. I am very happy with this freelancer and recommend him to anyone interested in label design/Amazon listing photos.

GREAT design. Fast delivery, no hassle. We weren’t sure exactly what we wanted, and are glad we went with the right person to envision the look and vibe this product needed. Somehow Asahab was able to know exactly what this project needed. Thank you so much! Ill be back
